[{"id":"099ace094320a3a1c08ae46a911b3da0","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: RFP -- First Amendment","date":"2007-12-31T20:10:34.000Z","formatted_date":"Dec 31, 2007","formatted_time":"8:10 PM","body":" \n \nDid I need to send this to ANdrew Farkas?\n \n \n \n \nLesley Groff\nExecutive Assistant to Jeffrey Epstein\n \n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Freddy de Jesus [mailto:freddy.dejesus@gmail.com] \nSent: Saturday, December 29, 2007 11:26 AM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nCc: Antonio J. Colorado\nSubject: RFP -- First Amendment\nImportance: High\n\n\n\nThe attached document is being sent on behalf of Antonio J. Colorado, Executive Director, Portal del Futuro.  \n\n \n\nFeel free to contact Mr. Colorado at 787-649-9426 if you have any questions regarding the content in the First Amendment to Request for Proposals Public-Private Partnership for Purchase and Development of former Naval Station Roosevelt Roads.\n\n \n\nYou can also find the document at Portal's website: www.portaldelfuturo.com <http://www.portaldelfuturo.com/> .  After entering the website, click on English then click on News/RFP.\n\n \n\nRegards,\n\n \n\nFreddy de Jes\u00fas\n\n \n\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\">\n<HTML xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\" xmlns:v = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:x = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel\" xmlns:p = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:powerpoint\" xmlns:a = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:access\" xmlns:dt = \n\"uuid:C2F41010-65B3-11d1-A29F-00AA00C14882\" xmlns:s = \n\"uuid:BDC6E3F0-6DA3-11d1-A2A3-00AA00C14882\" xmlns:rs = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:rowset\" xmlns:z = \"#RowsetSchema\" xmlns:b = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:p